  "date": "Sun, 26 Apr 2026 14:32:30 +0000",
  "snippet": "A shooter on Saturday threatened the president, his administration, and our country&#39;s free press. It was only the latest assault on the foundations of our way of life. ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏",
